snippet.title: Amber Heard, Shailene Woodley & Rooney Mara at The Art of Elysium Charity Gala 2018
snippet.description:
Coverage of The Art of Elysium Charity Gala 2018 with Amber Heard, Shailene Woodley, Rooney Mara, Victoria Justice, Joaquin Phoenix, River Phoenix, Rain Phoenix, Vanessa Hudgens, John Legend, Chrissy Teigen, Nikki Reed, Kristin Cavallari, Emmanuelle Chriqui, Dita Von Teese, Jordana Brewster, Rumer Willis, Mena Suvari, Ali Larter, Abigail Spencer, Cara Santana, & Madelaine Petsch,  on January 6, 2018.
